      "rationale": "FDA generic pump is a simplified surrogate geometry. Similarity metrics (Re, flow coefficient, specific speed) computed but VAD-specific features (volute geometry, secondary flow paths) not replicated in validation model. Relevance gap acknowledged but not quantified. Achieved level 2."
