      "acceptanceCriteria": "Systematic evaluation of turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive model form uncertainty with sensitivity study comparing at least two turbulence closures.",
      "rationale": "Only k-omega SST turbulence model used. No alternative turbulence closure comparison performed. Power-law hemolysis model selected without model-form sensitivity study. Epistemic gap; achieved level 1."
