      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters (fluid viscosity, density, hemolysis power-law coefficients C and alpha, RBC fragility) characterised with probability distributions and propagated via Monte Carlo.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed on five input parameters. Hemolysis power-law coefficient distributions sourced from dataset fda-pump-piv-hemolysis-2025q3 (dataVintage 2025-10-22), which predates the model revision of 2025-11-14. The blade-angle update altered near-wall shear stress distribution; the team asserted this change was not material to the power-law coefficient applicability without formal re-characterisation. RBC fragility distribution assumed Gaussian based on literature; device-specific characterisation not performed. Achieved level 2."
